data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully maintained 3BR/3BA half duplex in Shippensburg! End unit, first floor living with the option of having the primary on the main level or 2nd floor. Large living area, eat-in-kitchen with access to the back deck. Finished basement offers plenty of space for entertaining and storage! Attached one car garage. Close access to stores, downtown Shippensburg, and 81 access. Do not miss your opportunity to see this one!
